<h1 style="margin-bottom:0px;">Deployment modes</h1><div class="f14 metric" style="color:#656668;display:flex;"><img src="/assets/images/calendar.png" style="height:12px;margin-top:auto;margin-bottom:auto;"><span class="updateDate">&nbsp; Updated on 26/06/2019</span> &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; | &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <img src="/assets/images/updated.png" style="height:12px;margin-top:auto;margin-bottom:auto;"><span class="readTime">&nbsp; 2 minutes to read</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</div><br><div class="mw-parser-output"><p><br>
Before you proceed to the installation of the Operations Bridge, consider whether to deploy one or multiple master nodes. 
</p>
